that other brands like Pixel, Galaxy, and NOTHING have bad design, but I&amp;rsquo;m just here to talk
about Apple in particular today.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="spring-animations">Spring Animations
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>One thing many people will notice about Apple&amp;rsquo;s animation is that it&amp;rsquo;s just so smooth and bouncy.
As soon as you swipe-up-to-set-up, you are instantly greeted by your apps elegantly flying in and
bouncing off the &amp;ldquo;surface&amp;rdquo; of the home screen, that is, to convince your brain that the screen is 3D.&lt;/p>
